%% Client State Temporal Flow — Comeketo Agent
%% Per spec §16. How plans age, how comms invalidate them,
%% and where guardrails + approval cards interrupt the path to send.

flowchart TD
    Plan["05_seven_day_plan.md<br/>(strategy draft — NOT truth)"]:::plan --> Move["Next scheduled move<br/>(per plan)"]:::move
    Comms["New comms / transcript<br/>(01b_comms_verbatim.md updated)"]:::evidence --> State["State update<br/>(client_ledger.md)"]:::evidence
    State --> Check{"Plan still valid?<br/>(reply received?<br/>dates still ok?<br/>guardrails passed?)"}:::decision

    Check -->|"yes — no reply<br/>dates pass"| Guardrails["Run guardrails<br/>(comeketo-inbox skill)"]:::guard
    Check -->|"no — reply<br/>or dates stale"| Stale["Plan is stale<br/>· pause<br/>· re-audit before next send"]:::stale
    Check -->|"new transcript<br/>imported"| Rewrite["Rewrite or re-validate plan<br/>against verbatim file"]:::stale

    Stale --> Rewrite
    Rewrite --> Plan

    Guardrails --> Approval{"Risky move?<br/>(fee waiver, discount,<br/>scope promise, pricing<br/>claim, enrichment-based<br/>personalization)"}:::decision

    Approval -->|"no — boring-safe<br/>(nudge, confirmation,<br/>tasting reminder)"| Surface["Surface / send<br/>via comeketo-inbox skill"]:::send
    Approval -->|"yes — high risk"| Card["Isolated approval card<br/>(NOT batched)"]:::card

    Card --> Operator{"Operator<br/>approves?"}:::decision
    Operator -->|yes| Surface
    Operator -->|no| Hold["Hold<br/>· annotate plan<br/>· Open Problems entry"]:::stale
    Hold --> Plan

    Surface --> Log["Append to client_ledger.md<br/>+ activity.jsonl"]:::audit
    Log --> Wait["Wait for client response<br/>(Inactivity is a state)"]:::wait
    Wait -.->|"reply received"| Comms
    Wait -.->|"no reply,<br/>dates still pass"| Plan

    classDef plan fill:#fcd34d,stroke:#b45309,color:#451a03
    classDef move fill:#fde68a,stroke:#d97706,color:#451a03
    classDef evidence fill:#22c55e,stroke:#15803d,color:#052e16
    classDef guard fill:#ef4444,stroke:#991b1b,color:#fff
    classDef card fill:#dc2626,stroke:#7f1d1d,color:#fff,stroke-width:3px
    classDef stale fill:#fb923c,stroke:#9a3412,color:#fff
    classDef send fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
    classDef audit fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#5b21b6,color:#fff
    classDef wait fill:#cbd5e1,stroke:#64748b,color:#0f172a,stroke-dasharray: 4 3
    classDef decision fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#64748b,color:#0f172a
